These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: filmmaking, magic-tricks
The people have 2 different jobs:  project-manager, software-developer
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: ice-hockey, surfing
The people use 2 different means of transport: snowmobile, scooter
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
3. the project-manager is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Hobby       | magic-tricks       | filmmaking |
| Job         | software-developer | project-manager  |
| Sport       | surfing    | ice-hockey    |
| Transport   | scooter       | snowmobile      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: water, soy-milk
The people have 2 different jobs:  electrician, social-worker
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, comedy
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: volleyball, ice-hockey
1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the electrician is on the far left##1
3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk     | water |
| Job           | electrician | social-worker      |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy  | fantasy      |
| Sport         | volleyball | ice-hockey     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, sprite
There 2 different types of food: pepper, cabbage
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: hip-hop, classical
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, train
1. the fan of classical is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person drinking coffee is the person driving the train##1
3. the person eating pepper is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Beverage      | coffee | sprite  |
| Food          | pepper    | cabbage   |
| Music-Genre   | classical  | hip-hop   |
| Transport     | train     | bus |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
