There 2 different types of food: broccoli, pineapple
The people have 2 different jobs:  electrician, freelancer
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: hip-hop, funk
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left##1
2. the electrician is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
3. the person drinking sprite is the person eating broccoli##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | tea       | sprite |
| Food          | pineapple         | broccoli    |
| Job           | freelancer | electrician    |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop           | funk   |

