.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-10::.
There 2 different types of food: raspberry, grapes
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: techno, jazz
There are 2 different nationalities: nigerian, dutch
2 different pets are kept: cat, fish
1. the dutch is the owner of the fish##1
2. the fan of jazz is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
3. the dutch is on the right of the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |
| Food          | raspberry | grapes |
| Music-Genre   | techno     | jazz      |
| Nationality   | nigerian | dutch    |
| Pet           | cat    | fish    |

