.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  bartender, fisherman
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: epic, musical
2 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goat
The people use 2 different means of transport: snowmobile, subway
1. the bartender is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
2. the bartender is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is the fisherman##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Job           | fisherman | bartender     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic          | musical |
| Pet           | chinchilla          | goat    |
| Transport     | subway            | snowmobile       |

 